title: Terima Kedatangan Tim Red Sparks, Menpora Dito Harap Berdampak Besar untuk Voli Indonesia
description:
Menteri Pemuda dan Olahraga Republik Indonesia (Menpora RI) Dito Ariotedjo, menerima kedatangan perwakilan tim Red Sparks yakni Kepala Pelatih Ko Hee-jin serta perwakilan empat pemain Han Song-yi, Yeum Hye-seon, Park Eun-jin, Park Hye-min dan Megawati Hangestri Pertiwi di Ruang Kerjanya lantai 10 Kantor Kemenpora, Senayan, Jakarta, Rabu (17/4) siang.

Menpora Dito juga berharap selama berada di Jakarta untuk melakoni Fun Volley Ball dengan Indonesia All-Star, 20 April mendatang, Red Sparks bisa menikmati suasana di Jakarta dan sekitarnya.

Pelatih Kepala Red Sparks Hee Jin Ko, menyampaikan terima kasih atas sambutan hangat Menpora Dito dan jajarannya. Ia berharap kedepan olahraga dan industri bola voli Indonesia akan semakin maju.

title: Thumb corn—sweet and sticky corn that's only the size of a finger【滇西小哥】
description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

Having remained silent for over a century, it's time for it to be seen by the world! This is an old variety of glutinous corn from Xishuangbanna. In the past, due to its low yield and the underdeveloped state of internet and transportation, it was cultivated and consumed locally by the people of Xishuangbanna, with seeds being preserved from one season to the next. It is crystal clear, pocket-sized, adorable, soft, sticky, and sweet—all the praises one could give to corn, I wish to bestow upon it... Today, let's prepare a feast with the world's smallest corn!

title: Kronologi Terbaru Kecelakaan di Tol Cikampek KM 58
description:
Kecelakaan saat arus mudik di Tol Jakarta Cikampek KM 58 jalur contra flow, di Kabupaten Karawang, Jawa Barat, Senin (8/4/2024), berdampak pada tewasnya 12 orang dan dua orang terluka . Kecelakaan ini dipicu bus yang menabrak sebuah minibus yang alami kendala mesin. Berikut kronologinya.

Pukul 07.04 di Tol Jakarta-Cikampek (Japek) mobil minibus Daihatsu Gran Max dari arah Jakarta memasuki jalur contra flow (lawan arah) yang sudah dibuka pihak kepolisian untuk memperlancar arus mudik. Tak lama kemudian, mobil tersebut mengalami kendala mesin dan hendak menepi ke bahu jalan yang ada di sisi kanannya.

Saat akan menepi, dari arah berlawanan melaju sebuah bus yang tidak bisa menghindar, dan akhirnya menabrak mobil tersebut hingga terbakar. Karena insiden benturan itu bus berhenti secara mendadak dan kendaraan yang ada di belakangnya, Toyota Rush tak bisa menghindar dan menabrak bagian belakang bus, lalu menghindar ke kiri dan menabrak grand max hingga ikut terbakar.

Akibat kejadian ini, contraflow di Tol Japek dari arah Cikampek ke Jakarta dihentikan. Para pengguna jalan tol diarahkan menuju ke jalur arteri. Semua korban dibawa ke RSUD Karawang.

Kecelakaan fatal di Tol Jakarta-Cikampek Kilometer 58, menambah daftar panjang kecelakaan saat mudik Lebaran di Jabar. Tercatat lima kendaraan mengalami kecelakaan sehingga mengakibatkan 16 tewas dan 31 lainnya luka-luka dalam empat hari terakhir.

title: MAHALINI - MATI MATIAN (OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO)
description:
Sukses menggelar beberapa konser Fabula baik di Indonesia dan Luar Negeri, Mahalini Raharja penyanyi sekaligus musisi asal Bali ini hadir kembali dengan karya terbarunya yang berjudul “Mati-Matian”. Single ini ditulis langsung oleh Andmesh Kamaleng dan Mahalini. 

Mati-Matian bercerita tentang seseorang yang sangat mencintai kekasihnya dan sudah “Mati-Matian” berkorban dan membela kekasihnya tersebut, namun yang ia dapatkan tidak sebanding dengan apa yang telah ia korbankan. Sehingga timbul perasaan penyesalan dari dirinya karena telah “Mati-Matian” demi kekasihnya tersebut. Single ini memiliki nuansa yang cukup mendalam ditambah ciri khas suara dari seorang Mahalini yang sangat menjiwai lagu-lagu yang dibawakannya. 

Potongan lagu ini sempat dinyanyikan sebait ketika Mahalini konser di Malaysia. Harapannya tentu  berharap single terbarunya ini dapat mewakilkan perasaan orang-orang yang telah berkorban demi orang yang dicintainya, namun malah di sia-siakan. “Buat kalian yang bucin tapi malah dikecewain, mudah-mudahan lagu ini bikin kalian merasa nggak sendiri yaa” ungkap Mahalini. 

Single terbaru Mahalini yang berjudul Mati-Matian sudah bisa dinikmati di seluruh digital platform streaming kesayangan kamu. Mahalini juga merilis Music Video dari “Mati-Matian” yang sudah bisa ditonton di channel Youtube HITS Records. Enjoy!

title: Rolly vs Pitbull HIGHLIGHTS: March 30, 2024 | PBC on Prime
description:
Mexican star Isaac “Pitbull” Cruz (26-2-1, 18 KOs) did his talking in the ring as he wrestled away the WBA Super Lightweight World Championship from Rolando “Rolly” Romero (15-2, 13 KOs) with an eighth round TKO triumph.
 
"I'm very happy and humbled to win this title for my family and for Mexico,” said Cruz. "I was prepared for this. I wasn't here to just fight. I was here to terminate him...I did my talking right here in the ring. And I did this not just for me, but for everybody that is here at T-Mobile Arena. There's going to be a Mexican champ at 140 pounds for a long time.”
 
After enduring pre-fight trash talk from Romero, it was Cruz who established his dominance early, connecting with a left hook to the top of the head that wobbled Romero badly in round one. Although Romero steadied himself and valiantly survived the round, he was never able to shake Cruz with his own power.
 
“We gave the fans a great fight,” said Romero. “Unfortunately, we came up short. I want to thank ‘Pitbull’ Cruz and all the fans that came out and made this a great event. I’ll be back.”
 
Back training with Ismael Salas for the first time since early in his career, Romero was able to show enough movement and ring savvy to push the fight into the second half. He also attempted to strategically hold and keep Cruz off of him, but was deducted a point in round five for excessively holding. Despite these efforts, he was once again hurt late in round seven, this time from an onslaught that began with a straight right hand to the head.
 
“I fought with the intention to leave the decision out of the judges’ hands,” said Cruz. “Mission accomplished.”
 
Romero again showed his mettle by making it to the bell, but early in round eight was met with another onslaught of power punches from the hard-charging Cruz. This time, the barrage was enough to force referee Thomas Taylor to waive off the fight 59 seconds into the round. Cruz’s dominance was reflected in the punch stats as he out landed (129-85) and was more accurate (36% to 25%) than Romero.
 
"I am not here just to be a dangerous fighter,” said Cruz. “I now have a title that is backing me up. So anybody that is available, I'll be ready."

description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

Could moss be eaten? This common organism found in rivers and ponds is rarely associated with delicacies. However, moss from the Lancang River has become a unique and eye-catching feature in Xishuangbanna's culinary scene. You won't get to taste this delicious spread, so how can I best describe the delights of Xishuangbanna moss to you? Perhaps by making the dishes look more appealing. Using ingredients from the countryside and striving for Michelin standards, this table's vibrant greenery reflects the bountiful growth of spring. I hope it brings you joy.
